@startuml notification-lifecycle
title Notification Dispatch Lifecycle

[*] --> Pending : Event Triggered (e.g., Case Approved)

Pending --> Templated : Localized Template Resolved
Templated --> Dispatched : Passed to External Adapter (SMTP/SMS)

Dispatched --> Delivered : Provider Confirmation Received
Dispatched --> Bounced : Invalid Recipient (Permanent Failure)
Dispatched --> Failed : Provider Downtown (Pending Retry)

Failed --> Templated : Exponential Backoff Retry
@enduml
